{"tid":2421544,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住UST蝻亞仔D飲食POST","createTime":"2021-02-24T14:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T23:08:51.000Z","uid":227275,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a01592f9616ae5f543d840e7a0219bc6676e10b","tid":2421544,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"每次UST蝻亞仔開POST都會比人問佢去左邊度打劫 老強左邊條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983480bb9038cfb422c7ec0fb861c83e9bd874e7","tid":2421544,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"eb9039f47576e53e29565eebeab18f4ff5771f61","tid":2421544,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T20:35:55.000Z","msg":"條撚屌日撚日幫去食鼎爺 幫襯條廢佬藍絲"},{"pid":"a052ad35811ef042f2877901d7b87f7b302d9daa","tid":2421544,"uid":362713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:08:51.000Z","msg":"早上10時半左右，紅磡發生搶劫案。兩名男子行經鶴園東街與紅磡道交界時，遭兩名蒙面賊人持刀襲擊，搶去兩個背囊；據報背囊內內有74萬美元。賊人得手後，跳上接應的白色私家車，車上有兩同黨，逃去無蹤；兩名事主一人為本地人，另一人為南亞裔，同告中刀相繼送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕到，現正追緝4名南亞匪徒，並在全港各主要道路採取「捷進行動」，搜捕賊人及賊車。其中黃大仙龍翔道、西九龍快速公路奧運站外，均可見警員穿著避彈衣和頭盔，荷槍實彈截查可疑車輛，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=d637076d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180921%2F58706789&h=f020ca1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180921/58706789</a>"}]}